# URL of the deployed Cloudflare Worker audio proxy (see wrangler.toml + worker/).
# Required for stream playback across CORS/HTTP streams and for the
# visualizer / EQ / AM-radio effects. Without it the app falls back to plain
# direct playback (HTTPS streams only, no visualizer).
#
# Local dev: copy this file to .env and fill in the value.
# GitHub Pages build: set a repository variable named VITE_WORKER_PROXY_URL
# (Settings -> Secrets and variables -> Actions -> Variables).
#
# Example:
# VITE_WORKER_PROXY_URL=https://static-fm-proxy.your-subdomain.workers.dev
VITE_WORKER_PROXY_URL=
